extends layout.pug 

block content
    h1 Welcome
    section
        p This is a simple project testing out implementing user authentication and authorisation using JSON Web Tokens.
        p #[a(href="/user/new") Click here] to go to the signup page and choose a username and password.
        p No frontend libraries used, all html is generated server-side with Pug and Express.
        p Passwords salted and hashed with bcrypt, users authorised with jsonwebtoken in cookies. User data saved with MongoDB.
